{
  "stem": "8725.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I, I-- during the night, yet, I went there, and I made it-- put the brooms and everything behind where was the smaller-- you know, made it like a storage place for-- so if the Gestapo would come, they'd say, that was a storage place.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the morning, I was serving the breakfast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I heard like cockroaches, the Gestapo was every place, searching, looking here, there, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My feet were just like rubber.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could not wait enough for them to eat and go out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So as soon as the major left and everybody, I took a pail with, with-- put it-- something to drink, something to eat, and told Schultz that I go clean Major's apartment.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was walking in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The doorway opened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, Major usually closes the door, but the door opened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as I was coming closer to the bathroom, young SS man coming out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well, I don't look Jewish, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So at least-- he looked at me, and I was-- I said, well, I'm sorry, in German, I did not-- I was surprised in Major's apartment, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I am coming to clean his room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he say-- saluted and danke schoen, fraulein, and he go out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I opened the win-- the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ida was sitting like a Buddha, like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You can see her through the-- because they were hearing, because they heard the whole night explosions, fires from the ghetto site, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he just-- he was waiting for me to come.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He went from his need, he needed pee-pee, I guess, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he did his business and walked out.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
